{"tid":1999780,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想問大家平時點幫主子護理口腔","createTime":"2020-05-03T11:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T14:11:06.000Z","uid":357387,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0cb082efcbf71e66d970208fcc7a139110470335","tid":1999780,"uid":357387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"主子今年八歲了，仲要係肥貓<br />\n佢呢幾日唔舒服，睇咗獸醫話有牙石同口腔發炎<br />\n遲啲要同佢驗血睇下適唔適合洗牙，因為要全身麻醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但呢段時間餵佢食藥之餘我想同佢護理口腔<br />\n我有上網睇過，但好多都係啲臺灣網站<br />\n想知大家會用咩潔牙餅或牙膏幫佢護理<br />\n感謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肥主子圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/86oXJtR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F86oXJtR.jpg&h=c1c2e2bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFAOQaD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFAOQaD.png&h=9b98fa72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"106dacc7afc5ac18f947665e07771e3ca742eafe","tid":1999780,"uid":357387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"推唔郁照推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc712c04f6fa7a55731b273db1e81fda2451f4c","tid":1999780,"uid":109754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"我用紗布加椰子油/牙膏幫貓貓刷牙<br />\n椰子油消炎"},{"pid":"ffc4a64b8f2c93b03010c6b1d4fe11cafcd3577f","tid":1999780,"uid":357387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc712c04f6fa7a55731b273db1e81fda2451f4c","tid":1999780,"uid":109754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"我用紗布加椰